{"tid":2206836,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"15歲少年縱火改判勞教中心 原審犯原則性錯誤","createTime":"2020-09-17T17:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T19:43:48.000Z","uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"84293c6088bd7caaac08dd93038c43d5c9663961","tid":2206836,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T17:52:18.000Z","msg":"一名15歲少年年初在元朗投擲汽油彈，早前被判感化18個月，律政司認為判刑太輕，提出覆核刑期。案件由高等法院上訴庭潘兆初、彭偉昌及彭寶琴三名法官處理，他們認為水佳麗判刑過輕，犯下原則性錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n在索取勞教中心、更生中心及教導所報告後，上訴庭決定取消他的感化令，判他入勞教中心。勞教中心會視乎犯人表現，羈留14-20歲犯人1至6個月；完成羈留後可能需要接受為期一年監管，包括遵守宵禁。"},{"pid":"a6222c4426b16619168e6ab6287b14889e805c00","tid":2206836,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T17:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcf46fc9a14216f63b62a4edc4c7bd71733d873","tid":2206836,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a6222c4426b16619168e6ab6287b14889e805c00","tid":2206836,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T17:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T17:57:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf799394842eab103f0b40a9a4702b7c69c40b82","tid":2206836,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T19:43:48.000Z","msg":"勞教中心=奧斯威辛集中營"}]}